name: Panzerkampfwagen-VI-Tiger-Ausfuhrung-H
title: Panzerkampfwagen VI Tiger Ausführung H
author: Mearsu
description: The Tiger I, a German heavy tank of World War II, operated from 1942 in Africa and Europe, usually in independent heavy tank battalions. It was designated Panzerkampfwagen VI Ausf H during development but was changed to Panzerkampfwagen VI Ausf E during production
